    <details>
      <summary>How was the discount rate determined?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">The {(discountRate * 100).toFixed(1)}% rate was derived using the Capital Asset Pricing Model (CAPM), adding the explicit 4.18% 10Y Treasury risk-free rate to the product of COF's Beta and a 5.5% Equity Risk Premium.</div>
    </details>
